    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved Gradation 2 vs. required Gradation 3) is mitigated by the conservative nature of the single ASTM F1717 test condition and the consistency of results across two independent laboratories. Overall credibility is sufficient to support regulatory submission for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw design.",
